OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fto the night with some clear periods,
OL,7,Fcloud generally thickening however
OL,8,Fwith perhaps a few outbreaks of light
OL,9,Frain early Saturday morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FAny light rain first thing
OL,12,Fshould quickly clear with warm sunny
OL,13,Fspells lasting throughout the day, but
OL,14,Fperhaps feeling a little cooler
OL,15,Ftowards the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
